description:
Ours is a big, open, and clean apartment in the heart of Williamsburg, Brooklyn. It's perfect for groups of friends or couples that are looking for a home base for their NYC vacation.  

The apartment is located 3 blocks (re three normal, clean, and responsive, Ivy league graduates (please excuse the last part, some people seem to care). If you need anything, just ask!

Thanks again for considering our place. Please reach out if you have any questions whatsoever.

We hope to see you soon!

space:
Living room:

There are two big plush couches to fall asleep on, a dining room table that seats 6, a kitchen island to keep the chef company, and two desks to get work done on if need be (we hope not for your sake).

Sleeping:

With three full sized beds and two big couches, it easily sleeps eight (2 ppl per bed + 2 couches). We have an extra blow up somewhere if you happen to need it.

MOAR Location: 

The apartment is located 3 blocks (re three normal, clean, and responsive, Ivy league graduates (please excuse the last part, some people seem to care). If you need anything, just ask!

Thanks again for considering our place. Please reach out if you have any questions whatsoever.

We hope to see you soon!
summary:
Ours is a big, open, and clean apartment in the heart of Williamsburg, Brooklyn. It's perfect for groups of friends or couples that are looking for a home base for their NYC vacation.  

The apartment is located 3 blocks (<5 minutes walk) from the Bedford L Stop, the first stop in Brooklyn.

With three full sized beds and two big couches, it easily sleeps eight (2 ppl per bed + 2 couches).

We hope to see you soon!
Brett, Tim, and Andy
